<div id="page_header">
	<p>Creative Commons Content + Easy Attribution = OpenAttributes</p>
	<p>Simple tools for a range of  platforms  so that re-using and attributing open content is as easy as cut and paste. </p>
</div>
		

<div id="page">
	<div id="slider">	

		
